{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/ETME_Header_01_600x80.png?t=1736290845\" />Master the full potential of a varied party of heroes, composed of multiple classes and talents. Apply a multitude of skills and learn how to combine them to edge out an advantage against overwhelming odds and elevate your strategy with every conquered challenge. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/ETME_GIF_03_Chaos.gif?t=1736290845\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/ETME_Header_02_600x80.png?t=1736290845\" />Leverage the Real-Time Pause system to coordinate, combine, and maximize your party\u2019s potential to unleash tactical devastation on your enemies. Counter seemingly unwinnable life-and-death scenarios by using your wits to execute complex strategies in a heartbeat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/ETME_GIF_04_Fire.gif?t=1736290845\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/ETME_Header_03_600x80.png?t=1736290845\" />\u2026and ice, and oil, and fire, and poison. But no hazard can\u2019t be used to your advantage. Utilize your party\u2019s skills, items, and spells to turn the environment into a weapon against your enemies. Destroy explosive barrels, freeze, poison and burn your foes with cunning precision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/ETME_GIF_02_Attack.gif?t=1736290845\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/ETME_Header_04_600x80.png?t=1736290845\" />In its madness, the Empire used crystals to create absurd and cursed items. These artifacts imbue your party with additional strength and prowess while increasing the wielder\u2019s Instability.  Don\u2019t let it fester and grow, or you could lose that character forever.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/ETME_GIF_05_Vlad.gif?t=1736290845\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/ETME_Header_05_600x80.png?t=1736290845\" />Risk and reward are a core part of success when you try to Escape the Mad Empire. The choices you make as you explore, battle, and manage your adventuring party can be the difference between victory and defeat. Will you risk life and limb for the smallest of victories?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/ETME_Header_06_600x80.png?t=1736290845\" />\u2026 is doing the same thing over and over and expecting different results. Face every threat, taste victory and defeat, and learn from your mistakes. Attempt new strategies, builds, and synergies. Improve and experiment until you overcome every challenge in your way and <strong>answer the ultimate question:</strong> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/ETME_Header_07_600x80.png?t=1736290845\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736290845","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/page.bg.jpg?t=1736290845","capsule_image":"